{"tid":1107652,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"請人麻煩唔好咁仆街","createTime":"2019-04-15T11:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T01:03:21.000Z","uid":140587,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"20e47df2b00cb47d1e3f9da0e9a9d548ffaecc2e","tid":1107652,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅, 上個禮拜我同個fd一齊報更返event helper, 間公司就聲稱返齊8日先有位, 所以我同佢都報咗8日, 咁之後個更表係有我同佢嘅, 暫時未有問題<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/594ph50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F594ph50.jpg&h=3071b42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢亦都有確認更表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eh6wri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eh6wri.jpg&h=3508d29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係到咗前幾日無啦啦有個人要我send張相俾佢, 唔可以係證件相, 咁我以為係公司留record, 所以即時求其影張相俾佢就算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMFG4NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMFG4NO.jpg&h=82e5d396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到頭先無啦啦出咗個新更表, 係冇咗我個名同埋換咗第二個人上去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1NuueX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1NuueX.jpg&h=4b8c809a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f82FAU1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff82FAU1.jpg&h=baee0e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗我之外其他人嘅更係差唔多<br />\n<br />\n咁我問返個fd, fd個fd就話佢可能將啲相upload咗俾client揀, &quot;咁啱&quot;full咗人, 所以就冇我份<br />\n<br />\n真心講嘅, dllm。如果張相你哋係要send俾client嘅唔該你早啲講清楚, 我個樣或者張相太柒所以報咗8日更變0日都算, 但係自己張相俾咗其他人睇其實我就好撚介意嘅, 同埋係要攞張相去做filter嘅話我可能就唔會求其影。唔該你哋要請人同時要將個人資料俾公司以外嘅人就講聲先, 唔好咁不負責任。"},{"pid":"e97c6d834fe09ff2f7cd588317aee59e609993dd","tid":1107652,"uid":22309,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"到底有幾樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0c3c86c0cf8f1be1dd1bb07902978271f383df","tid":1107652,"uid":24378,"like":3